{"tid":646603,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友話我唔夠保護佢","createTime":"2018-04-29T07:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T05:15:12.000Z","uid":12618,"like":2,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f8d5f4e5f053ed4e5cbfa315ea1653f126627acd","tid":646603,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T07:55:24.000Z","msg":"等巴士果陣我女朋友係站度坐<br />\n我就企佢正前面<br />\n女朋友無端端拍一拍我<br />\n之後我女朋友就企左起身<br />\n<br />\n原來有個麻甩佬企係我女朋友後面不特止<br />\n仲要mark撚大個脾隻腳放係欄杆上<br />\n好似黃狗射尿咁既姿勢<br />\n而射尿個位就係對正我女朋友<br />\n如果我女朋友一擰頭就對正條麻甩佬碌鳩個位<br />\n<br />\n佢就一邊屌鳩我話我做咩唔話佢知叫佢起身唔好坐<br />\n又話我因爲我遲到比佢鬧 嬲佢所以唔通知佢<br />\n又話如果佢比人非禮我都會唔出聲乜乜乜<br />\n佢又話好想分手<br />\n<br />\n我係咪真係做錯左無通知佢/無好好保護佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"888b70d1ce4e43d4743b270ac90b01dcb9466921","tid":646603,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T08:05:12.000Z","msg":"你地點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e785da43675536b7fe9925b9d7942ed1709e83","tid":646603,"uid":287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T08:06:27.000Z","msg":"企到好近？ 我指個麻甩佬"},{"pid":"8e5a64ab07279d2802a6296dcb40a679c2c179ae","tid":646603,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T08:06:51.000Z","msg":"呢度一億唔夠再問我攞，呢刻開始你自己保護自己啦，我唔會再保護你"},{"pid":"16638169593419d53d02d87a2acf6aa62fde0c9b","tid":646603,"uid":44277,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T08:07:09.000Z","msg":"咁都留意唔到你的確有啲問題"},{"pid":"2792791b3ef27d01621bd5a71c1f02fb1283b8bf","tid":646603,"uid":137843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T08:07:24.000Z","msg":"咁你點解唔同佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b569ac05ca25e3104bd3c57a0ac2b5df2a2dad6f","tid":646603,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T08:07:38.000Z","msg":"咁撚閪寸？"},{"pid":"463a0215ae0055a344f33a9